    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
      <p>The records of the University of Michigan Center for Human Growth and Development (CHGD) date from 1963 to 2007 and divided into the five series: Reports, Committees, Administration, Publications and Visual Media.</p>
    </scopecontent>
